title: Phish - PMCLP 1993 Part 2  (Pretty Much Complete Live Phish)
description:
This is a repost of a Demonoid torrent, "Pretty Much Complete Live Phish" (PMCLP).  Basically, it is a catalog of "pretty much" every Phish show in circulation from 
before 10/07/2000 (Phish ended their first hiatus on 12/31/2002, and henceforth all recordings have been available via LivePhish).  Some are SBD, but by far mostly 
AUD; all have recording info; all are tagged, and even have artwork which corresponds to the venue; NONE of this is in FLAC:  This is exactly how this torrent was seeded 3 or 4 years ago.  Some are 320, but most are lower bitrates.  But the point is that many - if not most - of these recordings are not available at bt.etree.org...but if they are, I heartily suggest you head over there and download that and any other shows you like in wonderful FLAC.  If I find that any of these 
shows are available via bt.etree.org in FLAC I will upload that as well.  I am offering this collection up because it is comprehensive:  it really does comprise almost every Phish show in circulation from before the first hiatus.  I am really anal about FLAC/320 just like most of you, but the vast majority of these shows offered here are not presently available in the bittorrent community in any other format (although, once again, some are available at bt.etree.org, and some though Phish.com).

This is the second of at least 100 torrents which comprise the whole collection, which goes from 1984 - 2000.  

Here are the shows included in this installment, 1993 part 02:

1993-02-15 Memorial Hall, University of North Carolina, Chapel Hill NC (AUD)
1993-02-17 Benton Convention Center, Winston-Salem NC (AUD)
1993-02-18 Electric Ballroom, Knoxville TN (SBD)
1993-02-19 The Roxy, Atlanta GA (LivePhish)

1993-02-21 The Roxy, Atlanta GA (LivePhish)
